    "rationale": "Overall credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (Gradation 2 achieved vs. 3 required) is offset by the strong output comparison results across N=11 specimens at two independent laboratories and the conservative acceptance bounds applied. The model is accepted for use in the stated COU.",
